sequenceDiagram
    participant Caller as MCP Wrapper / Test Caller
    participant Executor as BridgeToolExecutor
    participant Catalog as CompiledBridgeToolCatalog
    participant Policy as IToolExecutionPolicy
    participant Approval as IToolExecutionApprovalService
    participant Tool as PreviewDocumentUpdateTool
    participant FS as Explicit Target File
    participant Audit as IAuditSink
    participant Log as RecordingBridgeLogger

    Caller->>Executor: ExecuteAsync bridge.previewDocumentUpdate requestId=request-123 operationId=operation-456
    Executor->>Log: Bridge tool execution started
    Executor->>Log: Redacted request payload
    Executor->>Catalog: TryGetTool bridge.previewDocumentUpdate
    Catalog-->>Executor: Descriptor and tool instance
    Executor->>Log: Manifest and capability metadata
    Executor->>Policy: EvaluateAsync ToolExecutionSecurityContext
    Policy-->>Executor: Allow
    Executor->>Approval: Not invoked because ApprovalRequirement=NotRequired
    Executor->>Tool: ExecuteAsync explicit targetPath plus expected state and replacementContent
    Tool->>Tool: Validate repo-relative path and reject traversal or wildcards
    Tool->>FS: Read only explicit target file
    FS-->>Tool: Current content
    Tool->>Tool: Compare expected content or SHA-256 hash
    Tool->>Tool: Detect PreviewGenerated, NoOp, DriftDetected, or InvalidRequest
    Tool->>Tool: Build deterministic unified diff when changed
    Tool-->>Executor: BridgeToolResult previewOnly=true
    Executor->>Log: Bridge tool execution completed
    Executor->>Log: Redacted result payload
    Executor->>Audit: RecordAsync DocumentPreview envelope
    Executor-->>Caller: Structured preview result with preserved correlation
